a from a direct numerical simulation of inertial particles suspended in\nNavier-Stokes turbulence to validate the arguments presented in this study.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 15 Jan 2015 22:39:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-06"}
