iderably\nsmaller and the transport of C$^{6+}$ not affected up to an appreciable extent;\nand in TJ-II the potential shows a moderate impact despite of the large\namplitude of $\\Phi_1$ for the parameters considered.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Jan 2015 12:48:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-01-19"}
