s on the achievable\nconstraints. In particular we analyse the feasibility of using the SKA1\nautocorrelations to probe the large-scale signal.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Jan 2015 14:33:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-24"}
